Additive Inverse of $$x$$
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='font-size:140%;']
$$-x$$<br/><br/>$$x+(\red{-x})=0.$$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_frontspeak]
Additive inverse of x
  [/ctns_frontspeak]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
The additive inverse of x is negative xx plus negative x equals zero.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

